# Per-session artifacts produced by /socratic:think (or any session writing here).
# Session-local, not part of the plugin.
.socrates/

# Original design doc — kept locally for reference, not part of the distributable plugin.
prd.md

# Defensive: in case a memory file/dir gets created inside the repo by mistake.
